**Bomber** | Neutral Killing
__Basics__
When there is no other bomb active, the **bomber** may place a bomb on a player during the night. At the end of the following night, the bomb will explode, dealing a *basic attack* to the player and all other players visiting them.

__Formalized__
End Night: Apply `Bomb` to @Selection (~Persistent) [Quantity: %Number%, Condition: not (@(AttrSelf:Bomb) exists)]
Passive: Win [Condition: @All->Count is 1]
